(Minimum MVP states) Tj T*
(- draft) Tj T*
(- sent) Tj T*
(- delivery_failed) Tj T*
(- in_progress) Tj T*
(- completed) Tj T*
(- cancelled) Tj T*
(- superseded) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Report lifecycle relationship) Tj T*
(Report status and work order status should not be the same thing.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Report status is citizen-facing:) Tj T*
(new -> accepted -> assigned -> in_progress -> resolved -> closed) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Work order status is operational:) Tj T*
(draft -> sent -> in_progress -> completed -> verified/closed) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(A report should become in_progress when at least one required work order is active.) Tj T*
(A report should become resolved only when required work orders are completed or verified.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Important rules) Tj T*
(- Work orders should usually be created manually by Conductor or Tenant Admin after a report) Tj T*
(is accepted.) Tj T*
(- Automatic routing can suggest the responsible entity, but should not silently send a work) Tj T*
(order.) Tj T*
(- Sent PDFs must be immutable snapshots.) Tj T*
(- Regenerating a sent PDF should create a new document version.) Tj T*
(- Reassigning after send should usually supersede/cancel the old work order and create a new) Tj T*
(one.) Tj T*
(- Email failure must not lose the work order.) Tj T*
(- Failed delivery should be visible and retryable.) Tj T*
(- Closing a report while work is active should be blocked or require Tenant Admin override) Tj T*
(with reason.) Tj T*
(- Duplicate merge should require special review if either report already has active/sent) Tj T*
(work orders.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Audit events required) Tj T*
(- work_order.created) Tj T*
(- work_order.updated) Tj T*
(- work_order.status_changed) Tj T*
(- work_order.assigned_entity_changed) Tj T*
(- work_order.pdf_generated) Tj T*
(- work_order.pdf_regenerated) Tj T*
(- work_order.email_queued) Tj T*
(- work_order.email_sent) Tj T*
(- work_order.email_failed) Tj T*
(- work_order.email_retried) Tj T*
(- work_order.cancelled) Tj T*
(- work_order.superseded) Tj T*
(- work_order.completed) Tj T*
(- work_order.verified) Tj T*
(- work_order.reopened) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Actions requiring a reason) Tj T*
(- cancel work order) Tj T*
(- reassign after send) Tj T*
ET
endstream
